/* OrderMapper.getShopAvailablePointAmt: 고객의 현재 사용 가능한 보유 포인트 합계 조회 */
SELECT COALESCE(SUM(CPB.RMN_AMT), 0)
  FROM CUSTOMER_POINT_BASE CPB
 WHERE CPB.CUST_NO = #{custNo}
   AND CPB.RMN_AMT > 0
   AND (
       CPB.EXPIRE_DT IS NULL
       OR CPB.EXPIRE_DT = '0000-00-00 00:00:00'
       OR CPB.EXPIRE_DT >= NOW()
   )

/* OrderMapper.countShopMypageCancelHistory: 쇼핑몰 마이페이지 취소내역 클레임 전체 건수 조회 */
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT OCB.CLM_NO)
  FROM ORDER_CHANGE_BASE OCB
 WHERE OCB.REG_NO = #{custNo}
   AND OCB.CHG_GB_CD = 'C'
   AND DATE(OCB.CHG_DT) >= #{startDate}
   AND DATE(OCB.CHG_DT) <= #{endDate}

/* OrderMapper.getShopMypageCancelHistoryList: 쇼핑몰 마이페이지 취소내역 클레임 목록 페이징 조회 */
SELECT OCB.CLM_NO
     , OCB.ORD_NO
     , DATE_FORMAT(OCB.CHG_DT, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%s') AS CHG_DT
     , OCB.CHG_STAT_CD
     , FN_GET_CODE_NM('CHG_STAT', OCB.CHG_STAT_CD) AS CHG_STAT_NM
     , COALESCE(OCB.PAY_DELV_AMT, 0) AS PAY_DELV_AMT
     , COALESCE(P.CNL_AMT, 0) AS REFUNDED_CASH_AMT
  FROM ORDER_CHANGE_BASE OCB
  LEFT JOIN PAYMENT P ON P.CLM_NO = OCB.CLM_NO
 WHERE OCB.REG_NO = #{custNo}
   AND OCB.CHG_GB_CD = 'C'
   AND DATE(OCB.CHG_DT) >= #{startDate}
   AND DATE(OCB.CHG_DT) <= #{endDate}
 ORDER BY OCB.CHG_DT DESC, OCB.CLM_NO DESC
 LIMIT #{pageSize} OFFSET #{offset}

/* OrderMapper.getShopMypageCancelHistoryDetailList: 쇼핑몰 마이페이지 취소내역 상품 상세 목록 조회 */ SELECT OCD.CLM_NO , OCD.ORD_DTL_NO , OCD.GOODS_ID , GB.GOODS_NM , OCD.SIZE_ID , OCD.QTY , OD.SALE_AMT AS SALE_AMT , COALESCE(OCD.ADD_AMT, 0) AS ADD_AMT , OCD.CHG_REASON_CD , FN_GET_CODE_NM('CHG_REASON', OCD.CHG_REASON_CD) AS CHG_REASON_NM , OCD.CHG_REASON_DTL , ( SELECT GI.IMG_PATH FROM GOODS_IMG GI WHERE GI.GOODS_ID = OCD.GOODS_ID ORDER BY GI.DISP_ORD ASC, GI.IMG_NO ASC LIMIT 1 ) AS IMG_PATH , ( SELECT GI.IMG_PATH FROM GOODS_IMG GI WHERE GI.GOODS_ID = OCD.GOODS_ID ORDER BY GI.DISP_ORD ASC, GI.IMG_NO ASC LIMIT 1 ) AS IMG_URL FROM ORDER_CHANGE_DETAIL OCD JOIN GOODS_BASE GB ON GB.GOODS_ID = OCD.GOODS_ID LEFT JOIN ORDER_DETAIL OD ON OD.ORD_NO = OCD.ORD_NO AND OD.ORD_DTL_NO = OCD.ORD_DTL_NO WHERE OCD.CLM_NO IN
#{clmNo}
ORDER BY OCD.CLM_NO, OCD.ORD_DTL_NO

/* OrderMapper.countShopMypageReturnHistory: 쇼핑몰 마이페이지 반품내역 클레임 전체 건수 조회 */
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT OCB.CLM_NO)
  FROM ORDER_CHANGE_BASE OCB
  JOIN ORDER_CHANGE_DETAIL OCD
    ON OCD.CLM_NO = OCB.CLM_NO
   AND OCD.ORD_NO = OCB.ORD_NO
 WHERE OCB.REG_NO = #{custNo}
   AND OCB.CHG_GB_CD = 'R'
   AND COALESCE(OCB.CHG_STAT_CD, '') != 'CHG_STAT_02'
   AND COALESCE(OCD.CHG_DTL_STAT_CD, '') != 'CHG_DTL_STAT_19'
   AND DATE(OCB.CHG_DT) >= #{startDate}
   AND DATE(OCB.CHG_DT) <= #{endDate}

/* OrderMapper.getShopMypageReturnHistoryDetailList: 쇼핑몰 마이페이지 반품내역 상품 상세 목록 조회 */ SELECT OCD.CLM_NO , OCD.ORD_DTL_NO , OCD.GOODS_ID , GB.GOODS_NM , OCD.SIZE_ID , OCD.QTY , OD.SALE_AMT AS SALE_AMT , COALESCE(OCD.ADD_AMT, OD.ADD_AMT) AS ADD_AMT , COALESCE(OD.SUPPLY_AMT, 0) AS SUPPLY_AMT , COALESCE(OCD.GOODS_CPN_DC_AMT, 0) AS GOODS_COUPON_DISCOUNT_AMT , COALESCE(OCD.CART_CPN_DC_AMT, 0) AS CART_COUPON_DISCOUNT_AMT , COALESCE(OCD.POINT_DC_AMT, 0) AS POINT_DC_AMT , OCD.CHG_DTL_STAT_CD , FN_GET_CODE_NM('CHG_DTL_STAT', OCD.CHG_DTL_STAT_CD) AS CHG_DTL_STAT_NM , OCD.CHG_REASON_CD , FN_GET_CODE_NM('CHG_REASON', OCD.CHG_REASON_CD) AS CHG_REASON_NM , OCD.CHG_REASON_DTL , ( SELECT GI.IMG_PATH FROM GOODS_IMG GI WHERE GI.GOODS_ID = OCD.GOODS_ID ORDER BY GI.DISP_ORD ASC, GI.IMG_NO ASC LIMIT 1 ) AS IMG_PATH , ( SELECT GI.IMG_PATH FROM GOODS_IMG GI WHERE GI.GOODS_ID = OCD.GOODS_ID ORDER BY GI.DISP_ORD ASC, GI.IMG_NO ASC LIMIT 1 ) AS IMG_URL FROM ORDER_CHANGE_DETAIL OCD JOIN GOODS_BASE GB ON GB.GOODS_ID = OCD.GOODS_ID LEFT JOIN ORDER_DETAIL OD ON OD.ORD_NO = OCD.ORD_NO AND OD.ORD_DTL_NO = OCD.ORD_DTL_NO WHERE OCD.CLM_NO IN
#{clmNo}
AND COALESCE(OCD.CHG_DTL_STAT_CD, '') != 'CHG_DTL_STAT_19' ORDER BY OCD.CLM_NO, OCD.ORD_DTL_NO

